    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You generate a field of lightning chakra as you perform a graceful dance. All creatures in your range must make a constitution saving throw, becoming shocked on a failed save until the end of their next turn.</p><p>If you have <em><strong>Lightning Release: Electric Boogaloo</strong></em> on your jutsu known list, you can target 1 of the creatures who failed their saving throw with this jutsu, casting it as a bonus action.</p>",
